  "lernziele": "<p>The ability of successful and competetive manufacturing of companies is heavily influenced by the development of advanced manufacturing technologies. The highly accuarte and complex parts with tight tolerances should be produced with high productivity, proper machine tools and faster time to market. These aims could be achived using advanced manufacturing technology and proper faclities and machine tools.&nbsp;<br />On successful completion of this module students will be able to to use advanced manufacturing technologies to improve the competitive advantage of the organisations.</p>",
