      "bezeichnung": "Advanced Metal Manufacturing",
      "lernziele": "<p>By the end of this module, the students will be able to&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>recognise a range of advanced manufacturing processes,&nbsp;</li>\n<li>undertsand the accuracy of machine tools and measurment systems,</li>\n<li>analyse advanced manufacturing technologies to determine their appropriateness for an application or process,</li>\n<li>analyse an existing manufactured product and associated process to introduce proposals for possible improvements.</li>\n</ul>",
      "planinhalt": "<ul>\n<li>Advanced machining</li>\n<li>Non-Conventional machining</li>\n<li>Sustainable manufacturing</li>\n<li>Additive manufacturing of metals</li>\n<li>Metrology</li>\n<li>Machine tools and their components</li>\n<li>Machine tools measurment</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
